verbose_text: The AgAS 's homologues from Norway spruce (Picea abies), isopimara-7,15-diene synthase and levopimaradiene / abietadiene synthase (PaLAS), produce isopimara-7,15-diene and a mixture of levopimaradiene, abietadiene, neoabietadiene, and palustradiene, respectively, when incubating with GGPP as substrate [XREF_BIBR].
